&lt;p&gt;An opportunity has arisen within the Health Visiting Service in Fishguard for an Admin Clerk. We are looking for an enthusiastic and motivated individual to provide general administration support to the Health Visiting Team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will possess excellent communication skills so as to sensitively handle telephone dialogue with patients and professionals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role will involve undertaking all administrative processes associated with patient activity and the post holder must be aware of the highly confidential nature of this role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will need to work across three sites; Fishguard, Crymych and St. Davids so will need to have the ability to travel between sites in a timely manner.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable for this post, English and/or Welsh speakers are equally welcome to apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Interviews will be held on 20th November 2020.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
